That's the somebody I know.

834
01:09:07,020 --> 01:09:09,050
And he cares, Frank.
He really cares.

835
01:09:13,530 --> 01:09:15,790
- You know what we're doing?
- Yeah.

836
01:09:15,870 --> 01:09:18,730
