is, like, a real investigation.

846
01:09:50,630 --> 01:09:53,760
And I am sure that the mayor
will see this immediately.

847
01:09:54,540 --> 01:09:56,700
McClain and Delaney...

848
01:09:56,770 --> 01:09:59,210
