891
01:13:14,570 --> 01:13:16,910
"Wow. Amazing!

892
01:13:16,980 --> 01:13:20,850
"Dynamite!
Beautiful! Dynamite!

893
01:13:20,910 --> 01:13:22,850
Priorities. Priorities."

894
01:13:22,920 --> 01:13:25,850
